                "invention-title": [
                    "Reforming hydrogen production integrated device",
                    "一种重整制氢一体化装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a reforming hydrogen production integrated device. The reforming hydrogen production integrated device comprises a combustor, a catalytic reactor, a reformed gas heat exchanger, a high-temperature CO converter, a low-temperature CO converter and a reaction raw material heat exchanger, the combustor and the catalytic reactor are of a coaxial structure and are arranged in a layered mode from inside to outside, and the reformed gas heat exchanger, the high-temperature CO converter, the reaction raw material heat exchanger and the low-temperature CO converter are of a coaxial structure and are sequentially arranged on the outer wall of the reactor in a sleeving mode from bottom to top. The reforming hydrogen production device has the beneficial effects that the whole reforming hydrogen production device is integrally designed, the structure is compact, the size is small, the hydrogen content in reformed gas is high, the CO content is low, the subsequent hydrogen purification process is integrated and simplified, the structure is compact, and the cost is reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种重整制氢一体化装置，包括燃烧器、催化反应器、重整气换热器、高温CO变换器、低温CO变换器、反应原料换热器；所述燃烧器、催化反应器呈同轴结构，从内向外分层布置，所述重整气换热器、高温CO变换器、反应原料换热器、低温CO变换器，呈同轴结构从下至上依次套装在反应器外壁上；本发明的有益效果是，整个重整制氢装置呈一体化设计，结构紧凑体积小巧，重整气中氢气含量高，CO含量低，有利于后续的氢气纯化工序集成简化，结构紧凑成本降低。"
                }
            ]
